    "wizard_content_next_btn": "Proceed zuwa na gaba abun ciki creation mataki mai jagora.",
    "wizard_find_standard_btn": "Bincika don educational mizani wancan match naka abun ciki topic.",
    "wizard_grade_option": "Zaɓi wannan matakin aji don naka darasi. Determines ƙamus da concept rikitarwa.",
    "wizard_growth_goal_input": "Shigar learning growth manufa don ɗalibi zuwa achieve tare da wannan abun ciki.",
    "wizard_instructions_input": "Ƙara na musamman umarni don AI zuwa follow lokacin generating darasi abun ciki.",
    "wizard_interest_add_btn": "Ƙara ɗalibi interest topic zuwa personalize samar abun ciki.",
    "wizard_interest_remove_btn": "Cire wannan interest topic daga personalization list.",
