      "framing_body": "simulators su ne imperfect approximations. They su ne useful don empathy-building da da sauri checks, ba don verifying compliance. protanopia tace shi ne ba same as protanopia. Real users yana da lived tare da their condition; kai su ne seeing it don 60 seconds. Yi amfani simulators zuwa surface obvious problems (launi-only bayani, low contrast, illegible rubutu), then jarrabawa tare da real users lokacin stakes matter.",
